text: David Garcia is an American politician and educator. He was the Democratic Party's nominee in the 2018 Arizona gubernatorial election. He lost to Doug Ducey. Garcia is an associate professor at Arizona State University's Mary Lou Fulton Teachers College. ==References== ==Other websites== * Garcia for Governor , campaign website Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Arizona State University faculty Category:Politicians from Phoenix, Arizona Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
